{"tid":972223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(天堂與地獄)  英小兄妹不知父遭中國籍母親殺害  妹妹抵英過新生","createTime":"2019-01-07T08:45:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T08:45:52.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2437e8ecb53553892a05a4118e89203f041204a5","tid":972223,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T08:45:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jHRCVlKjU5Ah6RiJz9uX.Q--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/961d367ddda8cb34860a9fecb826f89a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FjHRCVlKjU5Ah6RiJz9uX.Q--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F961d367ddda8cb34860a9fecb826f89a&h=c4e67e27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國連鎖時裝店Next的高層、長駐上海的辛普森，去年遭中國籍的分居妻子傅薇薇捅死。辛普森父母向女家支付9,200英鎊（約9.1萬港元），及經法庭審理後，只能帶走孫女艾麗絲，被迫遺下孫兒傑克在湖北南漳縣生活。艾麗絲抵達英國過新生活後不忘兄長，一對小兄妹每日靠視像通話，辛普森的父母則竭力爭取傑克的撫養權。<br />\n<br />\n艾麗絲抵達英國後重新學習簡單英語，又結識新朋友，且準備上學。從未與兄長分開的艾麗絲，在視像通話中興奮地與傑克分享即將去上學，她以普通話說：「希望你也在這裏幫溫功課。」傑克則答道：「我會來會合你，但首先要找到媽媽。」原來女家訛稱小兄妹的父母到海外工作，小兄妹並不知道母親殺了父親的事。<br />\n<br />\n辛普森的父親伊恩透露，未來數周將安排輔導員與艾麗絲見面，藉以告訴她父親已過身的事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B0%8F%E5%85%84%E5%A6%B9%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E7%88%B6%E9%81%AD%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B1%8D%E6%AF%8D%E8%A6%AA%E6%AE%BA%E5%AE%B3-%E5%A6%B9%E5%A6%B9%E6%8A%B5%E8%8B%B1%E9%81%8E%E6%96%B0%E7%94%9F-052011997.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%2585%2584%25E5%25A6%25B9%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%259F%25A5%25E7%2588%25B6%25E9%2581%25AD%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25B1%258D%25E6%25AF%258D%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E5%25AE%25B3-%25E5%25A6%25B9%25E5%25A6%25B9%25E6%258A%25B5%25E8%258B%25B1%25E9%2581%258E%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2594%259F-052011997.html&d=MmsljSwmbRLmMNnuRoW8H6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=d272e833\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B0%8F%E5%85%84%E5%A6%B9%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E7%88%B6%E9%81%AD%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B1%8D%E6%AF%8D%E8%A6%AA%E6%AE%BA%E5%AE%B3-%E5%A6%B9%E5%A6%B9%E6%8A%B5%E8%8B%B1%E9%81%8E%E6%96%B0%E7%94%9F-052011997.html</a>"},{"pid":"f1550754f7b72a27e909968d41724f92ee93ed26","tid":972223,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T08:45:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/小兄妹不知父遭中國籍母親殺害-妹妹抵英過新生-052011997.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E5%B0%8F%E5%85%84%E5%A6%B9%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E7%88%B6%E9%81%AD%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B1%8D%E6%AF%8D%E8%A6%AA%E6%AE%BA%E5%AE%B3-%E5%A6%B9%E5%A6%B9%E6%8A%B5%E8%8B%B1%E9%81%8E%E6%96%B0%E7%94%9F-052011997.html&d=MmsljSwmbRLmMNnuRoW8H6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=857f9b9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/小兄妹不知父遭中國籍母親殺害-妹妹抵英過新生-052011997.html</a>"}]}